OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales scoops prestigious
OL,4,Caward for TATA closure coverage
OL,6,FITV Cymru Wales has been recognised
OL,7,Ffor its coverage of TATA Steel's
OL,8,Fannouncement last year to begin the
OL,9,Fprocess of thousands of jobs losses in
OL,10,FPort Talbot.
OL,12,FThe Wales At Six team picked up the
OL,13,FNations and Regions award at the RTS
OL,14,FTelevision Journalism Awards 2025 last
OL,15,Fnight for a special dedicated half
OL,16,Fhour programme in January 2024 that
OL,17,Fwas broadcast from the steelworks and
OL,18,Fsurrounding community.
