OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales scoops prestigious
OL,4,Caward for TATA closure coverage
OL,6,FThe programme presented by Jonathan
OL,7,FHill saw raw reaction from
OL,8,Fsteelworkers about their uncertain
OL,9,Ffuture as well as challenging
OL,10,Finterviews with both TATA bosses and
OL,11,FWelsh Government ministers about their
OL,12,Froles in protecting the community.
OL,14,FThe coverage also went to Redcar, a
OL,15,Fformer steelmaking town which had been
OL,16,Fthrough similar circumstances.
