OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales scoops prestigious
OL,4,Caward for TATA closure coverage
OL,6,FAccepting the award last night, ITV
OL,7,FCymru Wales Head of News and
OL,8,FProgrammes Zoe Thomas said it was
OL,9,Ftestament to the importance of
OL,10,Fregional and national news,
OL,12,F"The award belongs to the entire team
OL,13,Fboth here and back in Wales, the
OL,14,Fbrilliant journalists, camera
OL,15,Foperators, editors, producers, and
OL,16,Feveryone who contributed to telling
OL,17,Fthis story, as well as those in the
OL,18,Fcommunity of Port Talbot who spoke to
OL,19,Fus at one of the most difficult times
OL,20,Fin their lives.
