OL,6,F"Regional and national news acts as a
OL,7,Fvital bridge, linking those
OL,8,Fcommunities, holding local and
OL,9,Fnational institutions accountable, and
OL,10,Fensuring that the voices of ordinary
OL,11,Fpeople are heard.
OL,13,F"This award is a testament to the
OL,14,Fdedication and sheer hard work of the
OL,15,Fentire team in Wales. It's a
OL,16,Frecognition of their commitment to
OL,17,Ftelling the stories that make a
OL,18,Fdifference, the stories that should
OL,19,Fand do matter to us all.
